      <h2>{{ site[locale].notifications.buttons.subscribe }}</h2>
      <div class="incidents-container">
        <ul class="list-reset">
          <li>
            <div class="incident under-maintenance unresolved scheduled">
              <div class="incident-header level-3">
                <div class="incident-title">
                  <h3>
                    Network Maintenance
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="incident-systems"><span class="badge">
                  API
                  </span><span class="badge">
                  CDN
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="incident-subtitle">
                <div><time datetime="2019-12-26T00:30:54.929Z">
                  Dec 26, 00:30
                  </time>
                  -
                  <time datetime="2019-12-26T01:00:54.929Z">
                  Dec 26, 01:00
                  </time>
                  (UTC)
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="incident-body">
                <div class="markdown">
                  <p>A network maintenance will be performed during 30 minutes. Short website access interruption is expected from this maintenance.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden">
                <svg version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 576 512" class="svg-inline--fa fa-w-12 ml-1 svg-icon svg-fill">
